description:
######1.2.0: Added backup feature, now you can send logs to your email, Added smiles.######

  ABOUT
•	Tracking your moods information helps you to control your psychological feelings and its many Health related issues.
•	The Mood Tracker simplifies mood data logging.
•	This app will allow you to enter the multiple mood logs at different times of a day.
•	 This app saves the Rating, Date and time and note.
•	This app will allow you to search logs by note.
•	Very easy to use.
  Features:
•	The intuitive interface for data logging.
•	Oversized numbers for easy data entry.
•	This app will allows you to send logs to doctor. 
•	Very simple and easy to use.
